IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Terry Wayne BAKER and Mary Elizabeth Baker Upon the Petition of Terry Wayne Baker, Petitioner-Appellant, And Concerning Mary Elizabeth Baker, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-2102 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Terry Baker appeals from the modification of the spousal support provisions of the decree dissolving his marriage to Mary Baker. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
